com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.model

Interface IBMECMSocialItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IBMECMBaseObject>, IBMECMBaseObject, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBMECMComment

    public interface IBMECMSocialItem
extends IBMECMBaseObject
    References a social item such as comments, tags, recommendations (or likes), and download records.

    For more information about the various types of social items, see IBMECMSocialItemType.
